{"tid":29271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]淑女台妹踩單車撞房車慘被 [2]","createTime":"2016-12-08T12:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T14:14:24.000Z","uid":1971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76803333b087cd69547fca87ec15d063376bc5b8","tid":29271,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">腳踏車PK凌志 網友：買菜大嬸完勝</span><br />\n<br />\n社會中心／綜合報導<br />\n還記得10月台中東海發生一起「BMW大七對決豐田ALTIS」的行車糾紛嗎？BMW大七完勝豐田ALTIS引發網友熱議，那當腳踏車對上LEXUS凌志百萬轎車，又會是什麼結果呢？<br />\n<br />\n▲凌志側邊被腳踏車撞凹一個洞。（圖／翻攝自爆料公社）<br />\n一名網友在臉書不公開社團《爆料公社》po照，寫著「買菜大嬸PK凌志」，照片中，一輛紅色淑女車直接撞上凌志轎車，車子的前保桿凹了一個洞，但腳踏車卻屹立不搖，毫髮無傷。這起車禍發生在今（7）日早上，57歲婦人騎腳踏車行經台北內湖康樂街口，與正要從停車場出來的轎車發生擦撞，婦人摔倒在地，但人沒大礙。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/TDv5RBYlcXCyGq3DzXQ12Q--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9NTEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/17dd51e2dee08ce9ac755c6231ff8d62\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FTDv5RBYlcXCyGq3DzXQ12Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9NTEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F17dd51e2dee08ce9ac755c6231ff8d62&h=d815aa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/YjSRr_0UhpTTukYCYvxAiA--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9NDA5/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/setn.com.tw/7d18820f40a9899356942fc2d072ea8a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FYjSRr_0UhpTTukYCYvxAiA--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9NDA5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F7d18820f40a9899356942fc2d072ea8a&h=8398c639&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好彩無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590e1ea5ce575095ff5d4eb7612c1ce20546b3f4","tid":29271,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T12:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset